      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great fit for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that doesn't need to be perfect. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small dents on the door panels, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all basic electronics and air conditioning remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, though it will likely need a brake service and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that reflects its mileage and age.",
