      "description": "Hey there! I am selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly maintained. It\u2019s looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You won't find a single flaw on this one! Come take a look, I promise you're going to fall in love with it.",
