    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2) in impeccable condition. This example features the sought-after F22C1 2.2L longitudinal inline-four, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline via VTEC engagement. The drivetrain remains factory-spec with a Torsen limited-slip differential and a crisp, close-ratio six-speed manual transmission exhibiting perfect synchro alignment. The chassis retains its high-rigidity X-bone frame integrity, supported by a precision-tuned double-wishbone suspension at all four corners. All VIN tags are present on original panels, confirming a no-incident history. Mechanicals are turn-key with zero fluid seepage or subframe oxidation. A definitive collector-tier roadster for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
