      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or fading. Every button feels crisp to the touch, and all electronic systems function flawlessly. Mechanically, it is faultless, having lived its life in a climate-controlled garage with a documented, open-checkbook maintenance history from the original dealership. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and completely silent. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been pampered by a single enthusiast owner.",
